$$A = \left[ {\matrix{
   {{e^t}} &amp; {{e^{ - t}}\cos t} &amp; {{e^{ - t}}\sin t}  \cr 
   {{e^t}} &amp; { - {e^{ - t}}\cos t - {e^{ - t}}\sin t} &amp; { - {e^{ - t}}\sin t + {e^{ - t}}co{\mathop{\rm s}\nolimits} t}  \cr 
   {{e^t}} &amp; {2{e^{ - t}}\sin t} &amp; { - 2{e^{ - t}}\cos t}  \cr 

 } } \right]$$
<br><br>$$\left| A \right| = {e^t}.\,{e^{ - t}}.{e^{ - t}}\left| {\matrix{
   1 &amp; {\cos t} &amp; {\sin t}  \cr 
   1 &amp; { - \cos t - \sin t} &amp; { - \sin t + \cos t}  \cr 
   1 &amp; {2\sin t} &amp; { - 2\cos t}  \cr 

 } } \right|$$
<br><br>Apply operations R<sub>2</sub> &lt; R<sub>2</sub> $$-$$R<sub>1</sub>, R<sub>3</sub> &lt; R<sub>3</sub> $$-$$ R<sub>1</sub>, R<sub>1</sub> &lt; R<sub>1</sub>
<br><br>$$\left| A \right| = {e^{ - t}}\left| {\matrix{
   1 &amp; {\cos t} &amp; {\sin t}  \cr 
   0 &amp; { - \sin t - 2\cos t} &amp; { - 2\sin t + \cos t}  \cr 
   0 &amp; {2\sin t - \cos t} &amp; { - 2\cos t - \sin t}  \cr 

 } } \right|$$
<br><br>Open the determinant by R<sub>1</sub>
<br><br>$$\left| A \right| = 5{e^{ - t}}$$
<br><br>Invertible for all t $$ \in $$ R
